        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Conjugate-Cam &#160;(</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Body-Closed Cam)</text> - a minimum of two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">2D-Cams</text> on a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text>, (e.g. a rotating <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Shaft</text>) that are each in continuous contact with a minimum of two <text styleclass="VariableName-small">follower-Rollers </text>on a different <text styleclass="Element">Part</text>. (e.g. an <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Oscillating Follower</text>).</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Groove Cam</text> is a special case of a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Conjugate Cam</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddConjugateCam-FB">Machine-Elements menu &gt; Add Conjugate Cam FB</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
